Introduction

YeonJi is a South Korean singer and dancer under MODHAUS.

On January 18, 2023, YeonJi was introduced as the twelfth member of the girl group tripleS under MODHAUS. She debuted with the sub-unit EVOLution on October 11, 2023, with the mini album "⟡". YeonJi then made her debut with tripleS on May 8, 2024, with the album "ASSEMBLE24".

As a member of tripleS, YeonJi was placed in the sub-units EVOLution and Visionary Vision.
